        "message": "Add files via upload\n\nDechunker is a custom tool developed by myself (and AI) to analyze JS files statically and extract Webpack Lazy Loaded JS files names. It works by giving the JS file URL as arg : ``` node .\\dechunker.js http://example.com/main.js ``` and give the list of all chunk names.\r\n\r\nNote: It may fails since this is not the final release but works on most cases.",
